{"tid":2128570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［大國勃起］西藏6.3級淺層地震 震央距拉薩600公里","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T07:31:48.000Z","uid":62856,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a3393a5f7c63f56edf9ce8c3a74089dc59dde3","tid":2128570,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"法新社引述美國地質調查所消息報道，地震發生在格林威治時間27日晚上8時7分（香港時間今晨4時7分），當地人口稀少。美國地質調查所表示，震央位於拉薩東北600公里左右，震源深度僅10公里。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國地震台網測定，這次地震發生地點為西藏昌都市丁清縣。近日西藏地震發生頻仍，過去5天皆有地震，其中一次發生在本月23日，規模達6.6級地震，地點為那曲市尼瑪縣。<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\nsouce：<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200728/PGS3ZX4TXEJOJ7JXNKITYSQTPM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200728%2FPGS3ZX4TXEJOJ7JXNKITYSQTPM%2F&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=844523ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200728%2FPGS3ZX4TXEJOJ7JXNKITYSQTPM%2F&h=34caab95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200728/PGS3ZX4TXEJOJ7JXNKITYSQTPM/</a>"},{"pid":"46b53652d369a1729926b9e7d6e0bcb053ded2f6","tid":2128570,"uid":149383,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"西藏咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可摸以震過少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2730641dc1f3d3f562421f0735bb55a09c31ce85","tid":2128570,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"又係長江流域<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72f21bb9c1e09ee33d8b4196b9a78c5974beaf6","tid":2128570,"uid":280136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"最重要係條長江<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" clas